RESOLUTION_NNP (_( 2_CD )_) 3_CD ._.
The_DT above_JJ figures_NNS show_VBP a_DT satisfactory_JJ increase_NN of_IN 25,287_CD in_IN the_DT number_NN of_IN out-door_JJ patients_NNS treated_VBN and_CC of_IN 155_CD in_IN their_PRP$ daily_JJ average_JJ attendance_NN ._.

4_CD ._.
The_DT total_JJ number_NN of_IN indoor_JJ patients_NNS admitted_VBN into_IN the_DT hospitals_NNS fell_VBD from_IN 26,058_CD to_TO 24,912_CD ,_, the_DT daily_JJ average_JJ attendance_NN also_RB declining_VBG from_IN 1,338.38_CD to_TO 1,281.36_CD ._.

1894_CD ._.
January_NNP 114_CD 4_CD February_NNP 268_CD 20_CD March_NNP 844_CD 44_CD April_NNP 541_CD 96_CD May_NNP 357_CD 82_CD So_RB far_RB as_IN these_DT figures_NNS go_VBP ,_, they_PRP seem_VBP to_TO afford_VB ground_NN for_IN the_DT surmise_NN that_IN the_DT epidemic_JJ reached_VBD its_PRP$ climax_NN in_IN the_DT high_JJ mortality_NN of_IN March_NNP 1895_CD ,_, and_CC is_VBZ now_RB tending_VBG to_TO abate_VB ._.
The_DT weekly_JJ mortality_NN shows_VBZ a_DT progressive_JJ decline_NN from_IN 233_CD ,_, the_DT number_NN of_IN deaths_NNS recorded_VBN in_IN the_DT week_NN ending_VBG 23rd_CD March_NNP ,_, to_TO 34_CD ,_, the_DT number_NN registered_VBN in_IN the_DT last_JJ week_NN of_IN May_NNP ._.
The_DT history_NN of_IN small-pox_JJ epidemics_NNS in_IN India_NNP generally_RB is_VBZ that_IN the_DT death-rate_JJ begins_NNS as_IN a_DT rule_NN to_TO decline_VB in_IN April_NNP and_CC May_NNP ,_, owing_VBG to_TO the_DT dry_JJ heat_NN of_IN these_DT months_NNS being_VBG adverse_JJ to_TO the_DT spread_NN of_IN the_DT disease_NN ,_, and_CC presenting_VBG conditions_NNS more_RBR favourable_JJ to_TO the_DT recovery_NN of_IN those_DT already_RB suffering_VBG ._.
This_DT rule_NN was_VBD found_VBN to_TO hold_VB good_JJ for_IN a_DT series_NN of_IN epidemics_NNS in_IN Calcutta_NNP ,_, except_IN only_RB those_DT of_IN 1832_CD and_CC 1878_CD ;_: and_CC in_IN more_RBR recent_JJ years_NNS it_PRP is_VBZ fully_RB borne_VBN out_RP by_IN the_DT statistics_NNS of_IN the_DT epidemic_NN of_IN 1890_CD ,_, and_CC in_IN a_DT less_RBR degree_JJ by_IN those_DT of_IN 1894_CD ._.
The_DT causes_NNS ,_, however_RB ,_, which_WDT produce_VBP an_DT epidemic_NN of_IN small-pox_NN are_VBP so_RB obscure_JJ ,_, and_CC the_DT spread_NN of_IN the_DT disease_NN depends_VBZ so_RB much_JJ upon_IN the_DT action_NN of_IN individuals_NNS ,_, that_IN all_DT attempts_NNS to_TO formulate_VB general_JJ conclusions_NNS or_CC to_TO forecast_VB the_DT course_NN of_IN events_NNS in_IN any_DT particular_JJ outbreak_NN must_MD be_VB for_IN the_DT most_JJS part_NN conjectural_NN ._.
Sir_NNP Charles_NNP Elliott_NNP can_MD only_RB hope_VB that_IN the_DT present_JJ epidemic_JJ is_VBZ now_RB beginning_VBG to_TO abate_VB ,_, and_CC that_IN the_DT lessons_NNS it_PRP has_VBZ taught_VBN will_MD not_RB be_VB lost_VBN upon_IN the_DT Corporation_NNP of_IN Calcutta_NNP ,_, who_WP are_VBP bound_VBN by_IN law_NN to_TO make_VB adequate_JJ and_CC suitable_JJ provision_NN for_IN preventing_VBG or_CC checking_VBG the_DT spread_NN of_IN dangerous_JJ diseases_NNS ,_, and_CC to_TO enforce_VB the_DT compulsory_NN provisions_NNS of_IN the_DT Vaccina-_NNP tion_NN Act_NNP ._.
8_CD ._.
The_DT number_NN of_IN admissions_NNS to_TO hospitals_NNS of_IN persons_NNS suffering_VBG from_IN cholera_NN was_VBD 567_CD against_IN 431_CD ,_, 709_CD and_CC 761_CD in_IN the_DT three_CD previous_JJ years_NNS ;_: and_CC 323_CD cases_NNS proved_VBD fatal_JJ ,_, giving_VBG a_DT death-rate_NN of_IN 56.9_CD per_IN cent_NN ._.

Fourteen_JJ cases_NNS of_IN cholera_NN originated_VBN in_IN the_DT Campbell_NNP Hospital_NNP ,_, of_IN which_WDT nine_CD proved_VBD fatal_JJ ,_, and_CC at_IN the_DT Howrah_NNP General_NNP Hospital_NNP a_DT European_NNP sailor_NN took_VBD the_DT disease_NN a_DT week_NN after_IN admission_NN ,_, and_CC died_VBD of_IN it_PRP ._.
In_IN neither_DT case_NN could_MD the_DT cause_NN of_IN the_DT outbreak_NN be_VB traced_VBN ,_, though_IN it_PRP is_VBZ suggested_VBN that_IN the_DT insufficiency_NN of_IN the_DT supply_NN of_IN filtered_JJ water_NN at_IN Sealdah_NNP may_MD have_VB led_VBN to_TO the_DT use_NN of_IN polluted_JJ tank_NN water_NN ._.

10_CD ._.
The_DT total_JJ number_NN of_IN major_JJ operations_NNS increased_VBD from_IN 3,339_CD to_TO 3,643_CD ,_, and_CC the_DT minor_JJ operations_NNS fom_VBP 19,001_CD to_TO 24,988_CD ._.

11_CD ._.
In_IN the_DT Eden_NNP Hospital_NNP ,_, 1,462_CD women_NNS and_CC children_NNS were_VBD treated_VBN ,_, against_IN 1,367_CD in_IN 1893_CD ._.

RESOLUTION_NNP (_( 2_CD )_) nose_RB ,_, under_IN Surgeon-Captain_NNP O'Kinealy_NNP ._.
The_DT increase_NN of_IN 216_CD at_IN the_DT Presidency_NNP General_NNP Hospital_NNP is_VBZ ascribed_VBN to_TO the_DT fact_NN that_IN the_DT out-door_JJ department_NN worked_VBD throughout_IN the_DT year_NN ,_, instead_RB of_IN for_IN nine_CD months_NNS only_RB ._.

The_DT numbers_NNS at_IN the_DT Mayo_NNP and_CC Chandney_NNP Hospitals_NNP rose_VBD by_IN 2,004_CD ,_, at_IN the_DT Chitpur_NNP Dispensary_NNP by_IN 1,505_CD ,_, at_IN the_DT Bhowanipur_NNP Dispensary_NNP by_IN 317_CD ,_, and_CC at_IN the_DT Howrah_NNP General_NNP Hospital_NNP by_IN 578_CD ._.

4_CD ._.
The_DT number_NN of_IN in-door_JJ patients_NNS rose_VBD from_IN 24,912_CD to_TO 26,879_CD ._.
The_DT increase_NN of_IN 1,967_CD was_VBD shared_VBN by_IN all_PDT the_DT hospitals_NNS except_IN the_DT Medical_NNP College_NNP ,_, where_WRB the_DT number_NN fell_VBD by_IN 93_CD ,_, and_CC was_VBD most_RBS marked_VBN at_IN the_DT Campbell_NNP and_CC Police_NNP Hospitals_NNP ,_, owing_VBG to_TO the_DT admission_NN at_IN the_DT former_JJ of_IN a_DT large_JJ number_NN of_IN small-pox_JJ cases_NNS ,_, and_CC in_IN the_DT case_NN of_IN the_DT latter_NN to_TO the_DT unusual_JJ prevalence_NN of_IN malarial_JJ fever_NN among_IN the_DT police_NN ._.
5_CD ._.
Including_VBG out-door_JJ and_CC in-door_JJ patients_NNS ,_, 178,982_CD men_NNS ,_, 45,764_CD women_NNS ,_, and_CC 68,805_CD children_NNS were_VBD treated_VBN during_IN the_DT year_NN ._.

8_CD ._.

2_CD ._.
Mortality_NN among_IN the_DT general_JJ population.2_NN REPORT_NNP ON_NNP THE_NNP Sanitary_NNP Commissioner_NNP to_TO examine_VB the_DT houses_NNS in_IN which_WDT it_PRP occurred_VBD ._.
I_PRP also_RB saw_VBD some_DT cases_NNS at_IN the_DT Medical_NNP College_NNP Hospital_NNP ._.
The_DT appearance_NN of_IN the_DT disease_NN caused_VBD much_JJ alarm_NN in_IN the_DT minds_NNS of_IN the_DT people_NNS who_WP fled_VBD from_IN the_DT city_NN in_IN large_JJ numbers_NNS both_DT before_IN and_CC after_IN Calcutta_NNP was_VBD officially_RB declared_VBN as_IN infected_VBN with_IN plague_NN on_IN the_DT 30th_JJ April_NNP ._.

4_CD ._.
Referring_VBG to_TO the_DT increase_NN in_IN the_DT death-rate_NN in_IN the_DT years_NNS 1895_CD ,_, 1896_CD and_CC 1897_CD in_IN Calcutta_NNP and_CC Howrah_NNP ,_, as_IN compared_VBN with_IN the_DT previous_JJ years_NNS ,_, His_PRP$ Honor_NNP the_DT Lieutenant-Governor_NNP desired_VBD ,_, in_IN paragraph_JJ 2_CD of_IN Government_NNP Resolution_NNP recorded_VBD upon_IN my_PRP$ report_NN for_IN last_JJ year_NN ,_, that_IN I_PRP should_MD closely_RB watch_VB the_DT present_JJ course_NN of_IN mortality_NN both_DT in_IN Calcutta_NNP and_CC Howrah_NNP and_CC promptly_RB communicate_VB to_TO Government_NNP any_DT unusual_JJ feature_NN that_WDT might_MD attract_VB my_PRP$ notice_NN ._.

5_CD ._.
The_DT causes_NNS of_IN increased_JJ mortality_NN in_IN past_JJ years_NNS in_IN Calcutta_NNP are_VBP probably_RB of_IN a_DT complex_JJ nature_NN ,_, into_IN which_WDT it_PRP is_VBZ unnecessary_JJ to_TO go_VB here_RB ,_, but_CC the_DT Sanitary_NNP Commissioner_NNP is_VBZ of_IN opinion_NN that_IN the_DT higher_JJR death-rates_NNS in_IN past_JJ years_NNS of_IN Howrah_NNP have_VBP been_VBN due_JJ to_TO some_DT extent_NN to_TO an_DT imperfect_JJ water-supply_NN ._.

This_DT Trust_NNP provides_VBZ houses_NNS for_IN artizans_NNS and_CC the_DT labouring_JJ poor_JJ of_IN London_NNP usually_RB in_IN lofty_JJ blocks_NNS of_IN build-_JJ ings_NNS ._.
In_IN 1898_CD there_EX were_VBD 11,367_CD rooms_NNS besides_IN bath-rooms_NNS ._.
The_DT mean_JJ population_NN during_IN the_DT year_NN was_VBD 19,562_CD ,_, showing_VBG a_DT density_NN of_IN 714_CD people_NNS to_TO the_DT acre_NN ,_, or_CC nearly_RB twelve_JJ times_NNS that_IN of_IN London_NNP ._.
Yet_RB the_DT birth-rate_NN for_IN the_DT year_NN was_VBD 33.1_CD per_IN 1,000_CD ,_, or_CC 3.6_CD above_IN that_DT of_IN all_DT London_NNP for_IN the_DT same_JJ period_NN ._.
The_DT death-rate_NN ,_, including_VBG deaths_NNS of_IN 54_CD persons_NNS removed_VBD to_TO hospitals_NNS ,_, was_VBD 14.7_CD per_IN 1,000_CD ,_, or_CC 4.0_CD below_IN the_DT average_NN of_IN London_NNP ,_, while_IN the_DT infant_JJ mortality_NN was_VBD 114.4_CD in_IN each_DT 1,000_CD births_NNS ,_, or_CC 52.8_CD below_IN that_DT of_IN London_NNP ._.
Overcrowding_VBG alone_RB is_VBZ therefore_RB not_RB the_DT cause_NN of_IN great_JJ mortality_NN ,_, because_IN the_DT risks_NNS attending_VBG it_PRP are_VBP greatly_RB diminished_VBN by_IN careful_JJ sanitation_NN which_WDT unfortunately_RB is_VBZ not_RB easily_RB applied_VBN in_IN what_WP are_VBP known_VBN as_IN the_DT bastis_NN in_IN Calcutta_NNP ._.
Happily_RB ,_, in_IN 1898_CD the_DT cholera_NN death-rate_NN was_VBD lower_JJR in_IN both_DT places_NNS than_IN it_PRP has_VBZ been_VBN for_IN the_DT 11-year_JJ period_NN ._.
Fevers_NNS gave_VBD less_JJR than_IN two-thirds_NNS of_IN the_DT mortality_NN of_IN 1897_CD in_IN Calcutta_NNP and_CC fell_VBD considerably_RB in_IN Howrah_NNP ;_: but_CC under_IN the_DT heading_NN ``_`` Other_JJ causes_NNS ''_'' there_EX was_VBD a_DT large_JJ rise_NN in_IN both_DT towns_NNS ._.
This_DT points_VBZ to_TO some_DT common_JJ cause_NN which_WDT has_VBZ not_RB been_VBN defined_VBN and_CC which_WDT clearly_RB indicates_VBZ that_IN our_PRP$ diagnosis_NN for_IN registration_NN purposes_NNS is_VBZ very_RB crude_JJ and_CC inefficient_NN ._.

6_CD ._.

Public_NNP Health_NNP in_IN the_DT Port_NNP of_IN Calcutta.4_NNP REPORT_NNP ON_NNP THE_NNP 1,161_CD in_IN 1898_CD ._.
This_DT deterioration_NN in_IN the_DT health_NN of_IN the_DT Police_NNP Force_NNP is_VBZ to_TO a_DT large_JJ extent_NN due_JJ to_TO the_DT fact_NN that_IN the_DT men_NNS stint_VBP themselves_PRP in_IN the_DT matter_NN of_IN diet_JJ to_TO save_VB money_NN ,_, and_CC I_PRP have_VBP accordingly_RB suggested_VBN during_IN my_PRP$ inspection_NN of_IN the_DT hospital_NN that_WDT ,_, as_IN in_IN Military_NNP lines_NNS ,_, their_PRP$ diet_NN should_MD be_VB examined_VBN by_IN their_PRP$ own_JJ officers_NNS ._.

5_CD ._.

6_CD ._.
